title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 25 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 25 2022
description:
Just because you live in a red state, doesn't mean you or your kids will avoid the liberal mask madness. Rand Paul pushes back against the school board of Jefferson County, Kentucky. Joining Clay and Buck, Jim Lamon, Army veteran, founder of DEPCOM Power, and battleground Arizona GOP Senate Candidate, discusses the daily invasion from our unprotected southern border. Fauci: Americans should wear masks in "schools, places of work," and any place "that brings people together in a closed environment." A 100-pound sailfish leaps from water, spears woman.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
